stone is hand-selected for color and clarity. The gold frame is cast using lost-wax technique and hand-finished in our NYC studio.</p><p>These earrings end just below the jawline \u2014 visible but delicate. The prehnite drop sways gently with movement. Comfortable for extended wear, light enough you may forget you have them on.</p>", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_details": {"type": "one_column", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Details & Materials", "heading_column_1": "Specifications", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<ul><li><strong>Material:</strong> 14k yellow gold</li><li><strong>Stones:</strong> Freshwater pearls (3\u20135mm), green prehnite cabochon drop (~10mm)</li><li><strong>Total Length:</strong> Approximately 3\u20134cm from earlobe</li><li><strong>Weight:</strong> Light enough for all-day wear</li><li><strong>Closure:</strong> Post with butterfly back</li><li><strong>Collection:</strong> Echoes</li></ul>", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_care": {"type": "one_column", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Care", "heading_column_1": "Jewelry Care", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p><strong>Gold & Pearl Pieces:</strong> Put jewelry on last, take it off first. Wipe with a soft cloth after wearing. Store in the provided pouch. Avoid perfume, chlorine, and harsh chemicals. Pearls benefit from being worn \u2014 natural skin oils maintain their luster.</p>", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_shipping": {"type": "two_column_tab", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Shipping & Returns", "content_vertical_alignment": "top", "column_spacing": 48, "heading_column_1": "Made to Order", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p>Every piece is handcrafted to order in NYC. Please allow 3\u20134 weeks for production. Free insured shipping on all orders. Signature required on delivery. You'll receive email updates during production and tracking when your piece ships.</p>", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text", "heading_column_2": "Returns & Warranty", "heading_font_class_column_2": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_2": "h3", "text_column_2": "<p>All sales are final \u2014 each piece is made specifically for you. 1-year warranty covers manufacturing defects. If your piece arrives damaged, contact us within 14 days with photos for repair or replacement.</p>", "text_font_class_column_2": "fs-body-100", "image_width_column_2": 100, "image_position_column_2": "above_text"}}}, "block_order": ["tab_description", "tab_details", "tab_care", "tab_shipping"], "settings": {"tab_alignment": "left", "tab_spacing": 40, "font_choice": "ff-heading", "tab_font_size": "fs-body-150", "background_color": "", "text_color": "#000000", "enable_animation": true, "section_padding": "section--vertical-padding-bottom-only"}, "disabled": false}, "multi-column": {"type": "multi-column", "blocks": {"column-1": {"type": "column", "settings": {"accent": "Handcrafted", "heading": "Made in NYC", "heading_tag": "h3", "heading_font_class": "fs-heading-3-base", "text": "<p>Every piece hand-carved, cast, and finished by skilled artisans in New York City.</p>", "text_font_class": "fs-body-300", "text_max_width": 100, "link": "", "link_text": "", "button_style": "btn--primary"}}, "column-2": {"type": "column", "settings": {"accent": "Natural Materials", "heading": "14k Gold & Pearls", "heading_tag": "h3", "headin